snippet.title: Let's Play Fallout 3 Van Buren
snippet.description:
If you don't know the long and crazy nature of Fallout 3 and Van Buren read up about it here: http://fallout.wikia.com/wiki/Van_Buren

If you would like to play this tech demo you can download it here: http://www.nma-fallout.com/article.php?id=35970

I've been wanting to do this video for months now and after numerous failures here it is!
Enjoy.
